/KeepColor {currentrgbcolor [/Pattern /DeviceRGB] setcolorspace} bind def
<< Tile8x8
 /PaintProc {0.5 setlinewidth pop 0 0 M 8 8 L 0 8 M 8 0 L stroke} 
>> matrix makepattern
/Pat1 exch def
<< Tile8x8
 /PaintProc {0.5 setlinewidth pop 0 0 M 8 8 L 0 8 M 8 0 L stroke
